location.fullValue: The Calgary Plan, The Hills at Rockbridge

data.description: Make this your new home in sought after neighborhood. Prime location just minutes from shopping area and 540 for your commute. This home features four spacious bedrooms with large bonus room that has window and closet which can be used as  a fifth bedroom. It has three full baths and one half bath. It has a large kitchen with center island. Lovely family room with fireplace. Trey ceiling in master bedroom. Covered patio in back and much more. For your recreation come enjoy the community pool. Come see it for yourself.
